Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.57,0:02:01.65,Regular,,0,0,0,,Bell Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.66,0:02:07.53,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Kaimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:09.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, Para-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.97,0:02:27.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone! We're slipping off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.48,0:02:33.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,They blew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:37.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,Another failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:39.11,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:52.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:57.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,Those two have been acting strangely lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:02:59.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,I wonder what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,That was totally Limone's fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.43,0:03:08.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,They let her join us because she was supposed to be a great prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.60,0:03:10.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Floe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.76,0:03:13.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for Aaeru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.49,0:03:31.41,Titles,,0,0,0,,White Solitude
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.08,0:03:43.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,I had hoped that Chor Tempest would have recovered by now, but they haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,You've seen what Chor Tempest is like now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.63,0:03:52.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,You were the only survivor from Chor Dextra. I'd like to hear your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.06,0:03:56.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,The situation certainly doesn't look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.81,0:04:02.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can see that they're a far cry from the elite choir that they once were.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:06.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,In their current state, they can barely handle daytime shifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:09.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like we'll be able to return them to night duty for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,We need them back at full strength right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.53,0:04:14.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why we called you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:17.71,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you do it, Sibylla Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.21,0:04:21.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and run checks on the helical motors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,And don't forget to clean the Simoun gems as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.43,0:04:33.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey! Limone, what were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:38.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't screw Aaeru up like that! If you're not going to do it right, you should quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.94,0:04:43.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,I... was told that I had to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.82,0:04:44.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:47.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.36,0:04:52.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're new, aren't you? Are you... Dominura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.37,0:05:00.87,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're Limone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.14,0:05:18.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Limone, your talent as a cadet was second to none.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.56,0:05:22.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,At the Academy, you broke most of the records for someone your age
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:28.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,both in written and practical tests, and you became the highest-ranked sagitta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:31.74,Regular,,0,0,0,,The Central Command recognized your abilities and made a special exception for you:
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:36.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,you were accepted as the youngest Sibylla in history,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:38.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,and assigned to Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.79,0:05:41.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,But you have zero experience in real combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.33,0:05:46.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,A few days ago, you went out on an unauthorized flight. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:47.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,Why are you asking?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:50.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Because I've taken an interest in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:57.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Needless to say, you have an outstanding record.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.47,0:06:02.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,The way Chor Tempest has ended up... doesn't it bother you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:07.73,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'll bet you never thought being a Sibylla would be like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.07,0:06:10.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:13.36,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,It won't be anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,All you have to do is listen to what I tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:23.75,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you do, you can go back to how things used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.92,0:06:27.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,You can reclaim the heights that a prodigy like you deserves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.42,0:06:34.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,Dominura seems to be using Limone to try to revive Chor Tempest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ah, well... taking care of the choirs is your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.89,0:06:40.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I don't understand that part.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:41.47,Regular,,0,0,0,,You don't understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,Let's just say...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.10,0:06:50.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,What those kids think is far beyond any adult's understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.82,0:06:55.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're talking about trying to understand the youngest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.45,0:06:58.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously telling me that you can do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.37,0:07:02.41,Regular,,0,0,0,,Guragief, let me tell you one thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.12,0:07:03.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.33,0:07:09.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,What we're doing out here... it's war.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:13.09,Regular,,0,0,0,,Even those kids understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.43,0:07:18.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.51,0:07:20.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.00,0:07:52.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, this is a surprise! I didn't expect you to come visit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.92,0:07:54.76,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.09,0:08:00.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,If we were to break up as a pair, how would that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.14,0:08:01.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:02.64,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:07.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,If that's what you want, it's fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.35,0:08:09.85,Regular,,0,0,0,,But I don't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.90,0:08:13.19,Regular,,0,0,0,,Was that all you wanted to ask me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:17.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,If I cut his hands off the controls...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.12,0:08:21.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,There's nothing else we can do, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.78,0:08:23.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:26.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, go wait over there, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.17,0:08:30.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hurry! Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:39.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Coming here wasn't because of any decision I made.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:43.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was just doing what other people told me to,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,and before I knew it, I was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:47.68,Regular,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:50.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I was hoping that you could tell me what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,What would you do if you were told to kill somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.07,0:08:56.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Um, I don't really know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.70,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to tell you what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.16,0:09:04.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm here because I'm trying to {\i1}avoid{\i0} making a decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.45,0:09:08.37,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you're afraid of fighting, it's okay to quit being a Sibylla.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:14.21,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you're not going to keep flying the Simoun, they aren't going to let you stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:22.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you really don't have a reason to stay here, you can always leave, can't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.28,0:09:37.61,Regular,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:48.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, you are so wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know you're going to be a splendid Simoun Sibylla someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:58.78,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, you need to be more considerate toward your teammates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.79,0:10:02.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,There isn't anyone who can follow you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.18,0:10:05.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're just a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.10,0:10:08.26,Regular,,0,0,0,,Don't butt in just because you can fly a little!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.48,0:10:16.06,Regular,,0,0,0,,I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:30.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, why don't you fly the Simoun any more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.37,0:10:33.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:35.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.25,0:10:37.38,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,Well, right now, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.17,0:10:46.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Sibylla Aurea, what in the world are we supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:49.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.23,0:10:55.77,Regular,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that you know what to do. Please, you must tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:04.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Right now... I don't have any strength to offer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:10.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:29.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.43,0:12:09.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,After all this time, I haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.86,0:12:30.12,Regular,,0,0,0,,A reconnaissance mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:34.66,Regular,,0,0,0,,There have been reports of possible large-scale military activities in the north.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.20,0:12:37.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,The north? From the Plumbum Highlands?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.08,0:12:42.84,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're more interested in how well Limone and Dominura are suited for each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.75,0:12:46.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,Alti and Floe are going with them as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.84,0:12:50.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,Did they become a pair?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.93,0:12:52.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,I've heard that Dominura decided that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.81,Regular,,0,0,0,,What kind of woman is she, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.94,0:13:00.94,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wait, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.02,0:13:01.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.19,0:13:04.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,You go over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.90,0:13:10.16,Regular,,0,0,0,,Me? The auriga?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.57,0:13:11.20,Regular,,0,0,0,,Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.49,0:13:13.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,This seat should be yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.62,0:13:14.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:17.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,I know all about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:20.46,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:22.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,If you know, then why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.79,0:13:24.25,Regular,,0,0,0,,As I said, it's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:27.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,Ever since that incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.05,0:13:30.80,Regular,,0,0,0,,you have been unconsciously suppressing your talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.93,0:13:31.97,Regular,,0,0,0,,I want you to set it free.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.80,0:13:36.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you that I know you better than anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.60,0:13:39.10,Regular,,0,0,0,,Just let me handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.14,0:13:42.23,Regular,,0,0,0,,Everything will be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.71,0:14:07.67,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.05,0:14:10.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,She had Limone fly as her auriga?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:12.72,Regular,,0,0,0,,It looks like she's up to something.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.14,0:14:24.69,Regular,,0,0,0,,How is it? Are you getting a feel for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.95,Regular,,0,0,0,,We'll be over the target soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.28,0:14:40.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Keep the communicator attached, and start the patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:41.04,Regular,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Hey, Limone, tell me something...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.35,0:15:00.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Can you really handle being an auriga?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.60,0:15:02.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,Or are you just doing as you're told again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:05.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,Cut the chatter, please, and focus on the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.98,0:15:09.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,And don't ever ask Limone a question like that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.57,0:15:10.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:20.54,Regular,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:21.83,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's snowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:30.42,Regular,,0,0,0,,It must be getting pretty cold out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.05,0:15:39.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,All clear to starboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:43.31,Regular,,0,0,0,,All clear dead ahead, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:04.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Enemy tanks! Three o'clock low!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.47,0:16:21.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,Wow, there are a lot of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.00,0:16:38.24,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're going in, too, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.28,0:16:40.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.50,0:16:47.29,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.09,0:16:53.59,Regular,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:56.01,Regular,,0,0,0,,Doing the Silver Ri Maajon all of a sudden is too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.09,0:16:57.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,No, I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.63,0:17:00.34,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's impossible! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.73,0:17:07.52,Regular,,0,0,0,,I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.19,0:17:14.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.00,0:17:33.63,Regular,,0,0,0,,Is she still holding on to what happened to her as a cadet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.93,Regular,,0,0,0,,This snow is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.35,0:17:46.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's a blizzard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:18:01.49,Regular,,0,0,0,,They're late. Shouldn't they be back by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.54,0:18:17.55,Regular,,0,0,0,,Oh! There are just too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.13,Regular,,0,0,0,,This situation is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:24.51,Regular,,0,0,0,,In this blizzard, we can barely even fly, let alone do a Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.51,0:18:30.56,Regular,,0,0,0,,If the two of us are having this much trouble, then that brand new pair...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.23,0:18:32.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, we have to withdraw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.10,0:18:35.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,We can't do anything if we can't draw a Ri Maajon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.61,0:18:39.44,Regular,,0,0,0,,This is a reconnaissance mission! We have to warn the others about this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.57,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:51.79,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:54.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:07.05,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.39,0:19:09.39,Regular,,0,0,0,,You're late, so we came to fetch you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.72,0:19:10.43,Regular,,0,0,0,,What's the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.02,0:19:12.48,Regular,,0,0,0,,We're withdrawing immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.14,0:19:13.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.15,Regular,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, Limone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.20,0:19:20.17,Regular,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.44,0:19:23.99,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone, listen to what I'm telling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.99,0:19:28.07,Regular,,0,0,0,,You need to figure it out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.33,Regular,,0,0,0,,Are you just doing what you're told again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:48.60,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:55.35,Regular,,0,0,0,,Silver Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.23,0:19:56.98,Regular,,0,0,0,,Limone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:59.27,Regular,,0,0,0,,Aaeru, let's do it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:02.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Roger that. We'll take them all out at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:06.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's suicide! Hardly anyone can do that Ri Maajon, and in these conditions...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.99,0:20:08.28,Regular,,0,0,0,,Silver Ri Maajon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:24.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's impossible! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.12,0:20:55.00,Regular,,0,0,0,,That's right! What I've wanted to do all along...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.46,0:21:02.50,Regular,,0,0,0,,is to make the most perfect Ri Maajons!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:48.22,Regular,,0,0,0,,She did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.22,0:21:50.88,Regular,,0,0,0,,All of the enemy tanks are destroyed?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.97,0:22:32.30,Regular,,0,0,0,,It's as I thought: that girl really is a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:36.18,Regular,,0,0,0,,So I wasn't wrong, after all...
